(# The 30-Day Jumpstart Guide) Tj
(## Get Clear. Get Prepared. Get Launching.) Tj
(---) Tj
(### What Is This?) Tj
(This is your 30-day action plan to go from "scared and uncertain" to "clear and ready.") Tj
(It complements the book "How I Fire'd Myself" but stands alone as a free resource.) Tj
(---) Tj
(### Who Is This For?) Tj
(- You're 50-65 years old) Tj
(- You've done the math but you're still scared) Tj
(- Your spouse isn't ready \(or you're not sure how to talk to them\)) Tj
(- You want to design your next chapter—not just stop working) Tj
(- You're ready to do the work) Tj
(---) Tj
(### The 30-Day Roadmap) Tj
(#### WEEK 1: GET CLEAR) Tj
(**Day 1: The Big Question**) Tj
(Ask yourself: "Am I leaving something, or going toward something?") Tj
(Write your answer in one sentence.) Tj
(**Day 2: The Fear Audit**) Tj
(Rate your top 3 fears from 1-10:) Tj
(1. _________________________________ \(___\)) Tj
(2. _________________________________ \(___\)) Tj
(3. _________________________________ \(___\)) Tj
(**Day 3: The Money Look**) Tj
(Calculate your current net worth:) Tj
(- Assets: $_____________) Tj
(- Debts: $_____________) Tj
(- NET WORTH: $_____________) Tj
(**Day 4: The Spouse Talk**) Tj
(Ask your partner: "What does your ideal day look like?") Tj
(Listen more than you talk.) Tj
(**Day 5: The Identity Check**) Tj
(Write down 5 things you're good at \(that aren't your job title\):) Tj
(1. _________________________________) Tj
(2. _________________________________) Tj
(3. _________________________________) Tj
(4. _________________________________) Tj
(5. _________________________________) Tj
(---) Tj
(#### WEEK 2: GET PREPARED) Tj
(**Day 6: The Budget Sketch**) Tj
(Write your three numbers:) Tj
(- Survival Budget: $_______/month) Tj
(- Comfort Budget: $_______/month) Tj
(- Freedom Budget: $_______/month) Tj
(**Day 7: The Stress Test**) Tj
(Ask yourself: "What's my biggest financial risk?") Tj
(Now ask: "Can I survive if that happens?") Tj
(**Day 8: The Social Scan**) Tj
(List your current social connections \(non-work\):) Tj
ET
