(- Family: ___) Tj
(- Friends: ___) Tj
(- Groups: ___) Tj
(- Community: ___) Tj
(**Day 9: The Build Plan**) Tj
(Pick ONE new activity to try this month:) Tj
(_________________________________) Tj
(**Day 10: The Vision**) Tj
(Close your eyes. Imagine it's 6 months after you left.) Tj
(What does your morning look like?) Tj
(Write for 2 minutes.) Tj
(---) Tj
(#### WEEK 3: GET MOVING) Tj
(**Day 11: The Numbers Conversation**) Tj
(Show your spouse ONE number \(not the whole spreadsheet\).) Tj
(Ask: "Does this make sense to you?") Tj
(**Day 12: The Exit Letter \(Draft\)**) Tj
(Write a letter to your career. Don't send it. Just write it.) Tj
(Include:) Tj
(- What you're grateful for) Tj
(- What you're leaving behind) Tj
(- What you're excited about) Tj
(**Day 13: The Curiosity List**) Tj
(Write 10 things you've always wanted to learn or try:) Tj
(1. _________________________________) Tj
(2. _________________________________) Tj
(3. _________________________________) Tj
(4. _________________________________) Tj
(5. _________________________________) Tj
(6. _________________________________) Tj
(7. _________________________________) Tj
(8. _________________________________) Tj
(9. _________________________________) Tj
(10. _________________________________) Tj
(**Day 14: The Network Reach**) Tj
(Text one person you haven't talked to in 6+ months.) Tj
(Say: "Hi! Just checking in.") Tj
(**Day 15: The "What Now" Answer**) Tj
(Practice answering: "What do you do now?") Tj
(Write 3 versions:) Tj
(1. _________________________________) Tj
(2. _________________________________) Tj
(3. _________________________________) Tj
(---) Tj
(#### WEEK 4: GET SOLID) Tj
(**Day 16-20: The Deep Work**) Tj
(Choose 3 topics from this list and go deeper:) Tj
(- [ ] Re-read your fear audit—has it changed?) Tj
(- [ ] Calculate your "freedom number") Tj
(- [ ] Research health insurance options) Tj
(- [ ] Update your estate documents) Tj
(- [ ] Join a new group/club) Tj
(- [ ] Schedule coffee with an old friend) Tj
(**Day 21: The Timeline**) Tj
(Write your target date:) Tj
ET
