(---) Tj
(### After 30 Days) Tj
(By now, you should have:) Tj
(- [ ] Clear vision of what you want) Tj
(- [ ] Identified your fears) Tj
(- [ ] Done the financial numbers) Tj
(- [ ] Had the spouse conversation) Tj
(- [ ] Started building your social plan) Tj
(- [ ] Picked your target date) Tj
(- [ ] Created your first milestones) Tj
(**Congratulations.** You've started your next chapter.) Tj
(---) Tj
(### Ready for More?) Tj
(Get the full book "How I Fire'd Myself" with:) Tj
(- 11 comprehensive chapters) Tj
(- Michael's complete story) Tj
(- 8 real case studies) Tj
(- Worksheets in every chapter) Tj
(- Appendices with templates and checklists) Tj
(- The Freedom Budget Calculator) Tj
(**[Get the Book →]**) Tj
(---) Tj
(### When to Get Help) Tj
(Consider professional help if:) Tj
(- You're overwhelmed by the numbers) Tj
(- Your spouse won't align) Tj
(- You're dealing with complex situations \(health, divorce, estate\)) Tj
(- You want a second opinion) Tj
(**Types of professionals:**) Tj
(- Certified Financial Planner \(CFP\)) Tj
(- Fee-only financial advisor) Tj
(- Retirement coach) Tj
(- Therapist/counselor) Tj
(---) Tj
(### Keep Going) Tj
(This is just the beginning.) Tj
(The journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step.) Tj
(You've taken the first step by downloading this guide.) Tj
(Now take the next step.) Tj
(**What's ONE thing you can do this week to move toward your next chapter?**) Tj
(Write it down. Then do it.) Tj
ET
